task.summary: First commit. Early prototype version. Major functionality -> 'publish a list' and 'get a list' works. Lots of tutorial boilerplate to be removed. Names of classes and functions have to be refactored.
On the GAE side: fetch_all() and get() work. Also display work. On local server side: publish(), fetch_all() and load_template() works.
On the GAE side: All functions necessary to process 'Publish', 'Update', 'Fetch' and 'Refresh' buttons work.
List and Scalar works. Data class is a common class for getting and fetching configurations.
Login, Logout and Register work. Before cleanup.
Login, Logout and Register work. After cleanup. Login/Logout and Register button works. @login_required applied to all required handlers.
